    researchFindings: ["The PURSUIT trial showed eptifibatide reduced the composite of death or MI by 10% versus placebo in acute coronary syndrome patients (NEJM, 1998).","The ESPRIT trial demonstrated a 37% reduction in ischemic events with eptifibatide during coronary stenting.","Pharmacodynamic studies confirmed >80% inhibition of platelet aggregation within 15 minutes of bolus administration.","Research showed platelet function recovers to near-normal levels within 4-8 hours of drug discontinuation.","Studies demonstrated eptifibatide has a more predictable and reversible antiplatelet effect compared to abciximab, the monoclonal antibody GP IIb/IIIa inhibitor."],
